parameters:
"As expected of a four-story building, there's an elevator.
But if I use it, they'll know I've broken in."

"Ah, damn it! Getting suspended on the first day of transfer
is just unbelievable! And it's all because of that shitty
girl!"

"Asahi Makoto... that bastard... just because I flirted with
a girl a little, she starts squawking and shrieking!"

"And on top of that, she calls me a pathetic man? How dare
she, a woman, get so uppity... I'll never forgive her."

"And the same goes for that guy who defended Asahi!!
Everyone's getting in my way!!"

"The students and teachers at that school!! All of them are
idiots and assholes!! It's so infuriating I feel like my
head's gonna burst!!"

"As per your instructions, young master, I've thoroughly
investigated Asahi. Everything from her home to her
commuting route to her circle of friends."

"Asahi is an exceptionally talented individual. Her grades
are always at the top, and it seems she has good athletic
abilities as well."

"She has a history of winning martial arts tournaments, and
not just the school, but there are many fans of hers
throughout the town."

"And about her family home... it's the Asahi Zaibatsu, known
to be one of the top conglomerates in the country."

"You're kidding me. I had no idea her parents were such big
shots. No wonder she's got a bunch of lackeys following her
around. What a worthless legacy."

"No, I'll continue. The mansion she lives in is located at
 street, , and that guy you punched, young master, seems
to be the neighbor of this house."

"That gloomy nerd, he was childhood friends with Asahi, huh.
That's why he had the gall to defend her."

"But this is perfect. If I can bring down Asahi, I can show
that nerd hell too."

"Right, are those two dating? It'd be more interesting if
they were..."

"No, it doesn't seem like they are in a relationship. They
go to school together every morning, but that's about it."

"What a drag. It would have been more fun to make them
despair if they were dating."

"Asahi usually spends a lot of time with friends. However,
she always goes straight home on Fridays."

"And tomorrow just happens to be Friday. If she has no
plans, she'll likely return home alone."

"Then that's perfect! Start tailing Asahi from tomorrow! If
it looks doable, snatch her up immediately!"

"There are several deserted spots along her route home. If
we're determined, we can easily abduct her even in broad
daylight."

"However, this time the opponent might be too much... If
we're not careful, we could be crushed by the Asahi
Zaibatsu..."

"...Hey, are you trying to give me orders? Are you also
trying to get in my way!?"

"Then shut up and just do it! My orders are absolute!! Got
it!!"

"And yeah, that reminds me!! Get \c[10]that drug\c[0] from
my old man again. Tell him we're not going to make a scene
this time, just in case."
"Understood. I will take my leave then."

"Kukukuku, just you wait, shitty Asahi. I'll show you
hell... no, heaven!!"

"Hehehe, kept you waiting, Asahi! Let's head straight to
bed!"
"Huh? What was that sound just now...?"

"Huh? What the, a blackout!? Damn, just when things were
getting good!!"
"The landline phone should be... over this way...?"

"...Damn, figures it's not working. Hey, Asahi! I'm going to
check the breaker, so wait here for me!"

"Hey, it's dangerous to walk around in the dark like
this..."

"As expected of a four-story building, there's an elevator.
But if I use it, they'll know someone has broken in."
